{
  "stem": "6966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had one here coming up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to one of my mates, look, I don't want to lay on the table again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh, I'll see to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took a crochet needle and killed the root on the inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I had to do because I was afraid of the doctors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a-- I got a operation in between my legs, probably from a kick from one of the kapos.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I couldn't help that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't walk, so  that had to be cut away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Auschwitz, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it's all in Auschwitz, what I'm saying, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now then, so one morning, I'm queueing up for a bandage for this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's a man in a white coat looking at all the men, all stripped naked queueing up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looking at the body, and he looks at me, and he takes my number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think nothing of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I goes to my bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the next morning, I'm called out of my bunk by the same man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He gives me a long coat, a pair of clogs, and I've got to follow him out of my barrack across into another barrack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I get into the barrack, I look, and I thought myself, this is a medical, medical department, clinic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I see tubes and bottles and instruments laying about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I s-- this doctor says sit down, so I sit down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's another doctor there, and those two are messing about with instruments and talking to one another.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyone was so-- I don't know what I'm doing here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- is this cold here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is this cold?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
